{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/iban","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"IBAN","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Međunarodni broj bankovnog računa (IBAN) je globalno prihvaćena metoda za identifikaciju bankovnih računa preko nacionalnih granica, sa manjim rizikom širenja grešaka prilikom unosa.</p>\n<p><abbr title=\"International Bank Account Number\">IBAN</abbr> Sastoji se od do 34 slova i brojeva:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>prvo dvosločani kod države od <abbr title=\"International Organization for Standardization\">ISO</abbr> 3166-1 alpha-2</li>\n  <li>zatim dva kontrolna broja, i</li>\n  <li>konačno Osnovni broj bankovnog računa (BBAN) specifičan za odgovarajuću zemlju.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Brojevi za proveru omogućavaju pametnu proveru broja bankovnog računa radi potvrđivanja njegovog integriteta čak i pre izvršavanja transakcije.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc7eaf","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napiši funkciju koja prima IBAN niz karaktera kao parametar. Ako je validan, vrati tačno. Inače, vrati netačno.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302289,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/iban"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function isValid(iban) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>isValid</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof isValid == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 32\")</code> Trebalo bi da vrati vrednost tačno ili netačno.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof isValid('GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 32') == 'boolean');"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 32\")</code> treba da vrati <code>true</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(isValid('GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 32'), true);"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"GB82 WEST 1.34 5698 7654 32\")</code> treba da vrati <code>false</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(isValid('GB82 WEST 1.34 5698 7654 32'), false);"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 325\")</code> treba da vrati <code>false</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(isValid('GB82 WEST 1234 5698 7654 325'), false);"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"GB82 TEST 1234 5698 7654 32\")</code> treba vratiti <code>false</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(isValid('GB82 TEST 1234 5698 7654 32'), false);"},{"text":"<p><code>isValid(\"SA03 8000 0000 6080 1016 7519\")</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>true</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(isValid('SA03 8000 0000 6080 1016 7519'), true);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"iban","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/identity-matrix","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/i-before-e-except-after-c","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc7eaf","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/iban"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}